## ğŸ—“ï¸ Meeting 4 â€“ Implementation & Integration

**Date:** Week 4  
**Participants:** Team  

### Discussion
Integrating the Roboflow model into a Python script proved challenging, particularly when retrieving the API key and inference URL.  
After several attempts and debugging sessions, the team successfully implemented a fully working inference pipeline.

### Decisions
- Final validation of the crack detection pipeline  
- Preparation of project artefacts and portfolio  

### Action Items
- Clean and comment the source code  
- Prepare final documentation  

